A

AirConcurrentMap<K,V> - Class in com.infinitydb.map.air
AirConcurrentMap is an extended multi-core ConcurrentNavigableMap and is faster and more memory efficient than any standard Java library Map and others for a wide range of use cases, especially large Map sizes.
